  "content": "<p data-pid=\"2gIyl2oG\">本系列专门介绍 SuperMemo 的各种小技巧和绕坑方法。</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/collection/797904700\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">SuperMemo tips</a><p data-pid=\"AY_U-dSL\">如果直接将网页内容粘贴到 SuperMemo，效果很可能是这样的：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-583b52b7d4b15c7767953baa18f8aa2e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1768\" data-rawheight=\"1256\" data-original-token=\"v2-583b52b7d4b15c7767953baa18f8aa2e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-387dc4cb22f660aca749eed41f30adac_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1768\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-583b52b7d4b15c7767953baa18f8aa2e_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1768&#39; height=&#39;1256&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1768\" data-rawheight=\"1256\" data-original-token=\"v2-583b52b7d4b15c7767953baa18f8aa2e\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-387dc4cb22f660aca749eed41f30adac_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1768\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-583b52b7d4b15c7767953baa18f8aa2e_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-583b52b7d4b15c7767953baa18f8aa2e_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-1247c65763872bbe826b78a4ed194b17_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1776\" data-rawheight=\"1256\" data-original-token=\"v2-1247c65763872bbe826b78a4ed194b17\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9168d0c4875da260e2b6a5707989ae7d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1776\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1247c65763872bbe826b78a4ed194b17_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1776&#39; height=&#39;1256&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1776\" data-rawheight=\"1256\" data-original-token=\"v2-1247c65763872bbe826b78a4ed194b17\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9168d0c4875da260e2b6a5707989ae7d_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1776\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1247c65763872bbe826b78a4ed194b17_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-1247c65763872bbe826b78a4ed194b17_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"u9yXd8Ry\">网页格式乱七八糟，如果能够统一，能够提高不少阅读体验。</p><p data-pid=\"6E-jCmno\">我推荐使用 Quicker 动作：</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//getquicker.net/Sharedaction%3Fcode%3D859bda04-fe78-4385-1b37-08d88a0dba1c\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-55118df3fb0656ecdfbede2bfe9fecdb_ipico.jpg\" data-image-width=\"160\" data-image-height=\"160\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">统一格式 - 动作信息 - Quicker</a><p data-pid=\"WK3mzlB6\">动图演示：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-2a10e003c1155e8372f4666c65d691ce_720w.gif?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1199\" data-rawheight=\"589\" data-original-token=\"v2-2a10e003c1155e8372f4666c65d691ce\" data-thumbnail=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-2a10e003c1155e8372f4666c65d691ce_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1199\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-2a10e003c1155e8372f4666c65d691ce_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1199&#39; height=&#39;589&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1199\" data-rawheight=\"589\" data-original-token=\"v2-2a10e003c1155e8372f4666c65d691ce\" data-thumbnail=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-2a10e003c1155e8372f4666c65d691ce_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1199\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-2a10e003c1155e8372f4666c65d691ce_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-2a10e003c1155e8372f4666c65d691ce_720w.gif?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"oV7Wq0eq\">还可以给 Quicker 动作绑定快捷键，就不需要通过面板操作了。</p>",
